headline: Garmin (NYSE:GRMN) Unveils Force Pro Trolling Motor And GFC 600H Flight Control For H130 Helicopters
summary: Garmin (NYSE:GRMN) recently announced several new product initiatives, including the Force Pro trolling motor and the GFC 600H flight control system, reflecting its ongoing commitment to innovation in the marine and aviation sectors. Over the last month, Garmin's share price increased by 4%, a robust performance amid broader market turbulence. This growth contrasts with the tech-focused Nasdaq Composite's decline of 1% and the S&P 500's nearly 1% drop, attributed in part to ongoing tariff...

headline: Meet some of the women Garmin is celebrating on International Women's Day
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) is celebrating International Women's Day by spotlighting some of the incredible female athletes and ambassadors who use Garmin products in their professions. From land to sea to air, Garmin makes products to fuel its customers' passions, and these women are excelling at just about everything.
